            "description": "<div><div class=\"sc-cOKnQQ dbCzjf\"><!--$--><h3 class=\"block core-block\">Gainers</h3><!--/$--><!--$--><ul class=\"block core-block\">\n<li><strong>Smart Share Global</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"EM\" style=\"display:inline-block\">EM</span> shares rose 25.1% to $1.47 during Friday's after-market session. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $296.7 million. </li>\n<li><strong>EZGO Technologies</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"EZGO\" style=\"display:inline-block\">EZGO</span> shares rose 10.16% to $0.41. The company's market cap stands at $2.0 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Star Equity Hldgs</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"STRR\" style=\"display:inline-block\">STRR</span> shares rose 7.98% to $2.3. The company's market cap stands at $7.0 million. As per the news, the Q2 earnings report came out 2 days ago. </li>\n<li><strong>Masterbeef</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"MB\" style=\"display:inline-block\">MB</span> shares increased by 4.78% to $3.72. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $74.8 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Algorhythm Holdings</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"RIME\" style=\"display:inline-block\">RIME</span> stock moved upwards by 3.44% to $2.4. The company's market cap stands at $6.1 million. </li>\n<li><strong>Petco Health and Wellness</strong> <span class=\"ticker\" data-exchange=\"NASDAQ\" data-ticker=\"WOOF\" style=\"display:inline-block\">WOOF</span> shares moved upwards by 3.29% to $3.45. The market value of their outstanding shares is at $954.1 million. </li>\n</ul><!--/$--><!--$--><h3 class=\"block core-block\">Losers</h3><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><p class=\"block core-block\">This article was generated by Benzinga's automated content engine and reviewed by an editor.</p><!--/$--><!--$--><div c